      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior has significant rust on the quarter panels and several deep dents, while the clear coat is peeling across the roof and trunk. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and the electronics are intermittent. Mechanically, it runs but requires immediate attention to the suspension and exhaust system. This would be an ideal project car or a source for parts for someone with the right tools.",
