    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a fantastic project or a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel? This vehicle is in poor condition and is ready for someone with a vision to give it the TLC and repairs it needs to get back on the road! It's a wonderful opportunity for a DIY enthusiast looking for a rewarding challenge at a great price.",
