      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle offers a showroom-quality aesthetic paired with flawless mechanical performance. Every detail has been meticulously scrutinized to ensure a peerless driving experience for its next owner. We invite discerning enthusiasts to acquire this masterfully preserved automobile, now available for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
